  "texts": [
    "This indicates that the agent's decision-making strategy has improved significantly when evaluated in the testing environment.",
    "Effectiveness and findings of this researchThis study presents an innovative traffic reduction system tailored for urban areas.",
    "Leveraging RL techniques, notably an advanced DQL algorithm, we have developed a system that operates on a reward-based mechanism.The premise is simple: when the queue length decreases, the agent gives a reward accordingly, incentivizing traffic optimization.",
    "Our results expresses the volumes about the efficacy of this approach.",
    "We have achieved a remarkable 49% reduction in queue length, translating to nearly a 50% decrease in waiting times-an impressive feat in traffic management."
